Painfully sincere Tweet: 

In 2012, I read a novel with unusually well-written women characters. Shot the author a Tweet, and developed a friendship. 

Season 5 of the TV about that book series just debuted. I’m just amazed with all @JamesSACorey has accomplished in 8 years.
